<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿们看着那个男人穿过了马路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须跟着他。”鲍比几乎叫了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们该报警吧？”赛伊不确定地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没时间了。快来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到左右都没车，鲍比跑过了马路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哥哥也跟了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人走得很快。他一直在看表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一定是要去见什么人。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩们藏在汽车的后面观察着那个男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在一辆深色的车前面停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车窗打开了，另一个扎着马尾的男人坐在车里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比指着那边叫道：“他要上车了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“车号是多少？”赛伊在找车号。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车子启动了，离开了这条街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我记下了车牌号。”赛伊说，“我们去找警察吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿们跑了又跑，终于找到了一位警官。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“警察叔叔！”他们大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哪里着火了？”警察笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和鲍比把他们看到的说了一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察不再笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去非常严肃，并写下了车牌号。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们的帮助。”警察说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，男孩儿们回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么这么久？”玛莎阿姨说着从赛伊手里接过了面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿们解释了刚刚发生的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇上的人们也听到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久之后，潘瑟领着一位警察走进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是之前和男孩儿们交谈过的那位警察。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们已经抓住了银行强盗。”他宣布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要谢谢这些男孩子们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察说着拍了拍男孩们的背。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和鲍比脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的邻居和男孩儿们又是握手又是拥抱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太为你们自豪了。”玛莎阿姨哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都离开后，孩子们一屁股坐到沙发上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面开始天黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得这里的人并没有那么坏。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但日落之后，他们就会忘记发生过的事情。”鲍比悲伤地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们会忘记关于我们的一切。”赛伊补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“至少我们知道这里的人很友善的。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看着太阳落山了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵急促的敲门声吓了他们一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊打开了门，是农夫詹金斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我拿来了一些自家做的果酱给我们的英雄。”他微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊？”鲍比一脸困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”潘瑟小心地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还记得他们欠农夫詹金斯多少果酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你们帮忙抓住了强盗。”詹金斯轻声笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你们喜欢这些果酱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把果酱罐递给赛伊后就走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们有些羞愧地看着那些果酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他为什么会记得抢劫的事情？”鲍比依然觉得困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着外面漆黑的天空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“休伊说太阳落山之后，一切都会回到原样的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没人可以解释这件事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，孩子们就去见休伊了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊刚把休伊从井里拉上来，鲍比就抛出了一连串的问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇哈！”休伊抬起了手，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你再说一次，你的愿望是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望发生一些好玩儿的事情。”鲍比回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后呢，事情发生了吗？”休伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天发生了一场银行抢劫。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那很可怕，不好玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还发生了其它的事情吗？”休伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们见到了很多以前不认识的人。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许银行抢劫并不是你们的愿望。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不明白。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“认识新的人感觉怎么样？”休伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们陷入了思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后鲍比回答。“有儿点意思。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许这才是你的愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊像魔术师一样张开了双手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这个愿望昨天就结束了。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们现在就不是我们的朋友了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那要看你们的了。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>